<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../style/bbt-mobile.min.css">
  <title>产检时间</title>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="bm-body">
    <div class="bm-panel">
      <div class="bm-feed-body">
        <div class="bm-feed-item">
          <img src="./images/baby.png" alt="baby" class="bm-feed-item-left">
          <div class="bm-feed-item-right-slogan">
            <p>宝贝，妈妈顺利完成本次产检啦</p>
            <p>妈妈会继续加油的</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bm-list-title">宝宝信息</div>
    <div class="bm-list-body">
      <div class="bm-list-item">
        <div class="bm-list-item-left bm-label-short">
          孕周
        </div>
        <div class="bm-list-item-right">
          <input type="text" class="bm-input" placeholder="请输入宝宝孕周">
        </div>
        <div class="bm-list-item-right-extra">
          周
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bm-list-item">
        <div class="bm-list-item-left bm-label-short">
          体重
        </div>
        <div class="bm-list-item-right">
          <input type="text" class="bm-input" placeholder="请输入宝宝宝体重">
        </div>
        <div class="bm-list-item-right-extra">
          公斤
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bm-list-title">温馨提示</div>
    <p class="bm-media-box-intro">妈妈孕前体重
      <sapn>xx</sapn>公斤，孕<span>1</span>周,体重正常增长值为xx-xx公斤，妈妈体重增长了xx公斤，妈妈控制得很好呢！</p>
    <div class="bm-btn-area">
      <button class="bm-btn bm-btn-primary" id="set-date">完成</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
